{"tid":295401,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"新緣份配對計劃 - 測試版第二回","createTime":"2017-06-23T17:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T06:28:27.000Z","uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"597b6fff93844cf356363a481c8d436a2f434371","tid":295401,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"新緣份配對計劃 - 測試版 第一回經已順利完結。<br />\n過程中多謝各位巴絲提供漏洞位置等我可以修復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一回結果已經由網站信息系統發放，如有幸進入第二回既巴絲理應會收到不少於2個信息，敬請留意。<br />\n<br />\n以下係第一回既數據：<br />\n<br />\n參加人數：886<br />\n男女比例：4:1<br />\n系統拒絕：443<br />\n<br />\n進入第二回人數：242<br />\n男女比例：3:1<br />\n組別：共25組<br />\n<br />\n系統拒絕 - 當系統檢測到有人惡意重覆參加就會自動取消所有參加資料。<br />\n組別 - 配對數字相同既為一組，姐係共有25組相同。<br />\n<br />\n第二回已經開始，有幸進入第二回既請係指定時間內去到網站信息系統選擇你心目中想配對既果一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只可以選擇一次 考慮清楚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可於網站首頁下方 點擊 新緣份配對計劃 - 測試版 第一回結果 進入信息系統。"},{"pid":"1733a3a715e4554dd741a3089627d9576bddaad6","tid":295401,"uid":12649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T17:28:32.000Z","msg":"想問下要係邊度回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe2ead3b749c059d38d4ea81aea21278cdee35f","tid":295401,"uid":24137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T00:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300f838129a7f291cf8f2510f7ab663e91ea3276","tid":295401,"uid":37022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T00:59:15.000Z","msg":"相joim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59045c2e9f9a038827ce444582c8d9585617767","tid":295401,"uid":37022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0